OL,3,CHolidaymaker glassed in bar fears
OL,4,Cbeing left blind for life
OL,6,FA man who was visiting family in the
OL,7,FUK for Christmas fears he will be left
OL,8,Fblind for life after being attacked
OL,9,Fwith a glass on a night out.
OL,11,FMatthew Syron, who is originally from
OL,12,FLeeds but now lives in Australia, was
OL,13,Fback in the city when his life was
OL,14,F"turned upside down" after he was
OL,15,Fattacked in Revolucion de Cuba bar.
OL,17,FHe was walking back from the toilet
OL,18,Falone when a man "glassed me and ran
OL,19,Foff".
