OL,3,CHolidaymaker glassed in bar fears
OL,4,Cbeing left blind for life
OL,6,FMr Syron said: "An arm came over my
OL,7,Fshoulder and shoved a bottle through
OL,8,Fmy face and followed me to the ground.
OL,9,FI could hear everything and I was
OL,10,Fconscious, but it's just black."
OL,12,FThe 32-year-old has already had
OL,13,Fsurgery on his eyes and has regained
OL,14,Fsome sight in his right eye.
OL,16,FBut he does not know if further
OL,17,Fsurgery will improve his sight.
