OL,3,CHolidaymaker glassed in bar fears
OL,4,Cbeing left blind for life
OL,6,FGareth Dean, 37, admitted grievous
OL,7,Fbodily harm with intent when he
OL,8,Fappeared at Leeds Crown Court on
OL,9,FThursday, 1 February. He will be
OL,10,Fsentenced on 4 March.
OL,12,FNow Mr Syron is calling for change by
OL,13,Fpetitioning to have similar rules
OL,14,Fbrought into UK law as the ones in
OL,15,FAustralia around safety in bars and
OL,16,Fclubs.
